    "description": "Health guide: Cat forbidden grape"
  },
  "hgCatForbiddenChocolate": "**Chocolate/Caffeine** — Heart and nervous system toxicity.",
  "@hgCatForbiddenChocolate": {
    "description": "Health guide: Cat forbidden chocolate"
  },
  "hgCatForbiddenRawFish": "**Raw Fish (continuous feeding)** — Causes Thiamine (B1) deficiency.",
